[SN]TITLE[SN]
US tornadoes: Aerial footage shows severe damage

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Buildings, including homes and churches, have been destroyed or severely damaged after a series of tornadoes struck southern US states.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 April 2016 Last updated at 07:40 BST
Several people were reportedly injured in Tulsa, Oklahoma, while the severe weather triggered fires in Odessa, Texas.
